          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Neither the object receiving this message, nor "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "observer"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", are retained. An object that calls this method must also eventually call either the "
